{"tid":1492034,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無絲打有多囊卵巢症同腺肌症？","createTime":"2019-08-20T15:57:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T16:24:00.000Z","uid":244573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6c121431edbff3b3f92aafecec5615256954a314","tid":1492034,"uid":244573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:57:10.000Z","msg":"2017年時我停咗避孕針開始爆瘡，仲要無m黎，之後去咗睇中醫經期正常翻。但仲有暗瘡所以去咗做婦科檢查，發現我有多囊卵巢症同腺肌症。醫生話我屬於輕微，問我黎m時有冇D乜嘢唔舒服，我話冇。再問我黎M前後會唔會容易出暗瘡，面比較油。我話呢樣有，仲生多左面毛，之後佢就建議我食避孕藥控制，話而家嘅避孕藥其實好輕劑量，話我依家不斷出暗瘡同埋有面油，係因為多囊卵巢症會引發雄性荷爾蒙增加，就算我去皮膚科食a算都冇用，因為身體入面嘅問題根本未解決。叫我唔好出到成塊面都係暗瘡嘅時候先來後悔唔食避孕藥。但我有樣嘢好矛盾，我當初係因為停咗避孕針開始係咁出暗瘡之後發現有呢兩個婦科病，而家醫生又建議我食返避孕藥，其實究竟食翻好定唔好？我之後又再去睇中醫調理但係睇完之後個瘤反而仲大咗少少。有無人可以解答下我？"},{"pid":"367991b50a28ae81e24973ae894b1803d094b4f7","tid":1492034,"uid":2562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:59:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PXcMrux.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPXcMrux.jpg&h=54112853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PN4V4gd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPN4V4gd.jpg&h=bf41982c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/20/233941_35db8952adc66a9b8fad2b475503a348.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F20%2F233941_35db8952adc66a9b8fad2b475503a348.jpeg&h=ba2d15e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0y2D12U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0y2D12U.jpg&h=c7bab806&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pYuV4gf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpYuV4gf.jpg&h=52b2bc94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tri4dee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftri4dee.png&h=7af3e96e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8ccd0e1444a28304f1